><br>Quest pieces (e.g. tears from HoT drakes) may be awarded to the participant who is nearest to completion. <br>Particular spells and items (e.g. Greater Remove Curse) that are of a tactical use for the guild may be awarded by the officers’ discretion based on the betterment of the guild. <br>Components quest keys (e.g. Trak tooth for VP) may be awarded by the officers’ discretion based upon availability and classes needed for a successful raid. <br>Epic components shall be awarded to the member who is nearest completion or banked until they are needed, unless the goal of the raid is to acquire specific component(s) for member(s).<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Multiple Characters</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br><br>Merit is assigned to each member for each account that member operates.<br><br>Raid capable characters on a single account share the same pool of merit points.<br><br>Raid capable characters on multiple accounts that can participate simultaneously use separate merit pools. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm17.showPrevMessage?topicID=9.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9.topic><img src=http://www.infinitusvindicat.com/images/f_addreply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm17.emailToFriend?topicID=9.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm17.threadControl?topicID=9.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator o